  "tiles": {
    "1": {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "## Spark System Metrics (aggregated)\nMirrors Grafana **Spark System Metrics**. Per-host drilldowns: **Host CPU Usage**, **Host Memory Pressure**, **Host Network Throughput**, **Host Disk Throughput**, **Host System Load**, **Host Hard Page Faults**, **Host GPU Metrics**, **Host GC Metrics**.\n\n**Phase 1 OTLP tiles** (bottom section): use a **2h** timeframe centered on a chapter run. **Active Executions** = stacked bars, 5s, `max(spark.executions.active.*)` — concurrent open executions (same semantics as Grafana Active Executions OTel). **Stage Shuffle** uses Grail counter keys `*.count` with `rate:1s`. **Stage Failures / Spill** use OTLP gauges (`spark.stage.outcomes.failures`, `spark.stage.outcomes.spill.*`); flat zero is valid when chapters do not fail or spill."
    },
    "2": {
      "type": "data",
      "title": "Average System Compute Use",
      "visualization": "lineChart",
      "subType": "dql-builder-metrics",
      "query": "timeseries cpu=avg(dt.host.cpu.usage)",
      "querySettings": { "enableSampling": false, "maxResultRecords": 1000, "maxResultMegaBytes": 1 },
      "visualizationSettings": { "autoSelectVisualization": false },
      "davis": { "enabled": false, "davisVisualization": { "isAvailable": true } }
    },
    "3": {
      "type": "data",
      "title": "Average System Memory Pressure",
      "visualization": "lineChart",
      "subType": "dql-builder-metrics",
      "query": "timeseries mem=avg(dt.host.memory.usage)",
      "querySettings": { "enableSampling": false, "maxResultRecords": 1000, "maxResultMegaBytes": 1 },
      "visualizationSettings": { "autoSelectVisualization": false },
      "davis": { "enabled": false, "davisVisualization": { "isAvailable": true } }
    },
    "4": {
      "type": "data",
      "title": "Total Network Throughput",
      "visualization": "lineChart",
      "subType": "dql-builder-metrics",
      "query": "timeseries {rx=sum(dt.host.net.nic.bytes_rx), tx=sum(dt.host.net.nic.bytes_tx)}\n| fieldsAdd tx = tx[] * -1",
      "querySettings": { "enableSampling": false, "maxResultRecords": 1000, "maxResultMegaBytes": 1 },
      "visualizationSettings": { "autoSelectVisualization": false },
      "davis": { "enabled": false, "davisVisualization": { "isAvailable": true } }
    },
    "5": {
      "type": "data",
      "title": "Total Disk Throughput",
      "visualization": "lineChart",
      "subType": "dql-builder-metrics",
      "query": "timeseries {read=sum(dt.host.disk.bytes_read), write=sum(dt.host.disk.bytes_written)}\n| fieldsAdd write = write[] * -1",
      "querySettings": { "enableSampling": false, "maxResultRecords": 1000, "maxResultMegaBytes": 1 },
      "visualizationSettings": { "autoSelectVisualization": false },
      "davis": { "enabled": false, "davisVisualization": { "isAvailable": true } }
    },
    "6": {
      "type": "data",
      "title": "Total System Load Trend",
      "visualization": "lineChart",
      "subType": "dql-builder-metrics",
      "query": "timeseries load=sum(dt.host.cpu.load)",
      "querySettings": { "enableSampling": false, "maxResultRecords": 1000, "maxResultMegaBytes": 1 },
      "visualizationSettings": { "autoSelectVisualization": false },
      "davis": { "enabled": false, "davisVisualization": { "isAvailable": true } }
    },
    "7": {
      "type": "data",
      "title": "Total GC Pause Time",
      "visualization": "lineChart",
      "subType": "dql-builder-metrics",
      "query": "timeseries gc_ms=sum(dt.runtime.jvm.gc.total_collection_time)",
      "querySettings": { "enableSampling": false, "maxResultRecords": 1000, "maxResultMegaBytes": 1 },
      "visualizationSettings": { "autoSelectVisualization": false },
      "davis": { "enabled": false, "davisVisualization": { "isAvailable": true } }
    },
    "8": {
      "type": "data",
      "title": "Total JVM Heap Used (GC reclaimed proxy)",
      "visualization": "lineChart",
      "subType": "dql-builder-metrics",
      "query": "timeseries heap=sum(dt.runtime.jvm.memory_pool.used)",
      "querySettings": { "enableSampling": false, "maxResultRecords": 1000, "maxResultMegaBytes": 1 },
      "visualizationSettings": { "autoSelectVisualization": false },
      "davis": { "enabled": false, "davisVisualization": { "isAvailable": true } }
    },
